==== Backup Methods ====

Automated Backup (Daily via Ansible):

Cron job on mgmt.lab.local:
0 2 * * * cd /opt/ansible/playbooks && ansible-playbook backup-homelab.yml

Playbook location: /opt/ansible/playbooks/backup-homelab.yml

Manual Backup (On-Demand):

Run all backups manually:
