In disaster scenario, restore in this order:

1. FreeIPA (mgmt.lab.local) - FIRST

    Provides authentication and DNS for entire lab
    Nothing else works without this
    Estimated restore time: 30 minutes


2. Nginx (apps.lab.local) - SECOND

    Provides reverse proxy for all web services
    Services accessible after this
    Estimated restore time: 15 minutes


3. Databases (apps.lab.local) - THIRD

