## SSL Certificates

Location: `/etc/nginx/ssl/` on apps.lab.local and mntr.lab.local

Files Backed Up: - `*.key` - Private keys (CRITICAL - store securely) - `*.crt` - Certificates - `*.csr` - Certificate Signing Requests - `ipa-ca.crt` - FreeIPA CA certificate

Backup Frequency: Nightly (included in Docker volume backups)

Security Considerations: - Private keys (*.key files) are sensitive - Store backups in encrypted location - Limit access to backup files - Never commit private keys to version control

Restoration:

```bash # Restore SSL directory from backup sudo tar -xzf backup.tar.gz -C /etc/nginx/ssl/

# Set correct permissions sudo chmod 600 /etc/nginx/ssl/*.key sudo chmod 644 /etc/nginx/ssl/*.crt

# Restart Nginx docker compose restart nginx

# Verify HTTPS works curl -I https://service.lab.local ```

